review.reviewBody: red velvet Red Velvet Cake with Vanilla Ice Cream is ok but Indian Coffee was great
According To restaurant it P2P Malai Rabri Shake but in reality it just a melted ice cream with pistachio toping totally scam not even close to P2P Malai Rabri Shake

i really appreciate your food and service that you are providing. Your dishes are highly commendable and appreciatable. i love each and every single dish that i have tried so far. Thanks for your good service and delicious taste.

Worst Chicken Malai Tikka -OO i have ever had at any restaurant. I asked for hot, it is blank, flavorless. And who makes a malai tikka with chicken breast. I guess they just had to fulfil an order, so they sent what they had.
Good taste but could be better and more like real Indian street food. Fries on the side was an extra treat. Spice level was kept as I asked (:
